											<p>SHAY Construction Pvt. Ltd. has established a legacy of premium construction and design through a rapidly growing customer base. Since 2021, we have achieved significant milestones, including the creation of over 1.2 million square feet of floor plates and the development of 65.3 acres of infrastructure. With over 45 projects slated for completion by the end of 2025, our journey is defined by a relentless pursuit of excellence and timely delivery.</p>
										</div>
										<div class="tab-thumb">
											<img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1109541/pexels-photo-1109541.jpeg" alt="">
										</div>
										<div class="tab-title">
											<h3>Precision Engineering</h3>
											<p>Our detailed focus ensures excellence across every project, from villas to multi-story buildings.</p>
										</div>
										<div class="prossess-ber-plugin pt-20">
