											<div id="bar1" class="barfiller">
												<div class="tipWrap">
													<span class="tip"></span>
												</div>
												<span class="fill" data-percentage="100"></span>
											</div>
											<span class="prosses-bar">Technical Expertise</span>
											<div id="bar2" class="barfiller">
												<div class="tipWrap">
													<span class="tip"></span>
												</div>
												<span class="fill my-class" data-percentage="92"></span>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div> 
									<div class="tabs_item">
										<div class="post-comment-description">
											<p>Our mission is to provide sustainable engineering solutions that prioritize longevity and resource sustainability. We aim to exceed customer expectations by ensuring their satisfaction is integral to everything we do.</p>
										</div>
										<div class="tab-thumb">
											<img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1109541/pexels-photo-1109541.jpeg" alt="">
										</div>
										<div class="tab-title">
											<h3>Precision Engineering</h3>
											<p>Our detailed focus ensures excellence across every project, from villas to multi-story buildings.</p>
										</div>
									</div> 
									<div class="tabs_item">
										<div class="post-comment-description">
											<p>To be a leader in the construction industry by adhering to the principle of precision in quality and leveraging cutting-edge engineering resources to achieve the highest standards.</p>
